{%- block heading %}
## SECTION {{ slNum }} (Maximum Marks: {{ maxMarks }}){.text-center}
{%- endblock %}

{%- block sectioninfo %}
- This section contains **{{ totalQuestions | toWords | upcase }} ({{ totalQuestions | zeroPad: 2 }})** questions.
{%- endblock %}
{%- block questioninfo %}
- Each question has **{{ answerOptions.rows.count | toWords | upcase }}** options {{ answerOptions.rows.chars | joinInEnglish: '(', ')' }}. **ONLY ONE** of these **{{ answerOptions.rows.count | toWords | downcase }}** options is the correct answer.
{%- endblock %}
{%- block eachquestion %}
- For each question, choose the option corresponding to the correct answer.
{%- endblock %}
{%- block markingscheme %}
- Answers to each question will be evaluated _according to the following marking scheme_:
  - |-----------------|---|-------------|
    | *Full Marks*    |&nbsp;:&nbsp;&nbsp;| {{ questionMarks.correct | prepend: "+" }} if **ONLY** the correct option is chosen; |
    {%- if questionMarks.incorrect == 0 %}
    | *Zero Marks*    |&nbsp;:&nbsp;&nbsp;| 0 In all other cases. |
    {%- else %}
    | *Zero Marks*    |&nbsp;:&nbsp;&nbsp;| 0 If none of the options is chosen (i.e., the question is unanswered); |
    | *Negative Marks* {.text-nowrap}|&nbsp;:&nbsp;&nbsp;| {{ questionMarks.incorrect }} In all other cases. |
    {%- endif %}
    {.no-border}
{%- endblock %}
